aa(lp165
V(Applause)
p166
aa(lp167
VJob training,
p168
aVmentoring,
p169
aVcounseling ...
p170
aVTeaching young people to learn from their mistakes
p171
aVinstead of criminalizing them,
p172
aVand dragging them out of their classrooms like animals.
p173
aVHow about this?
p174
aVI propose that we implement restorative justice in every high school in America.
